---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Impact"
  description="See MiMaji Foundation's impact across East Africa — communities served, people reached, and countries where we're creating lasting change in water access."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="hero-badge">Our Results</div>
    <h1>Our <em>Impact</em></h1>
    <p>Every number represents a life improved, a community empowered, a step closer to solving the water crisis across East Africa.</p>
    <svg class="hero-wave" viewBox="0 0 1440 100" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path d="M0,60 C360,100 720,20 1080,60 C1260,80 1380,50 1440,60 L1440,100 L0,100Z" fill="white"/>
    </svg>
  </section>

  <!-- Vision Image -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="vision-image fade-in">
        <img
          src="/modern-kenya-waterrefinery.png"
          alt="A modern Kenyan water refinery and treatment facility — the kind of infrastructure MiMaji Foundation supports through advocacy and partnerships across East Africa"
          loading="lazy"
          width="1200"
          height="600"
        />
        <p class="image-caption">What success looks like &mdash; modern, transparent water infrastructure serving every household in Kenya.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Honest Disclosure -->
  <section class="bg-sand">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Where We Are</div>
      <div class="section-title">Honest About Our Stage</div>
      <div class="honest-callout fade-in">
        <p class="honest-lead">MiMaji Foundation is in its <strong>pilot phase</strong>. We have not yet served thousands of people. We do not have years of impact data to point to. What we have is a clear plan, a small dedicated team, real research, and the conviction to build this the right way &mdash; from the ground up.</p>
        <p>The numbers below are our <strong>2026&ndash;2027 targets</strong>, not historical achievements. As we deliver each programme, we will publish actuals, methodology, and source data publicly. No inflation. No vanity metrics.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Focus Countries -->
  <section class="focus-section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Where We Work</div>
      <div class="section-title">Impact Across East Africa</div>
      <div class="section-subtitle">Our operations span 7 countries, each with unique water challenges and solutions.</div>
      <div class="focus-grid">
        <div class="country-list fade-in">
          <div class="country-item active">
            <span class="flag">🇰🇪</span>
            <div class="info"><h4>Kenya</h4><p>Phase 1 &bull; Pilot Active</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="country-item">
            <span class="flag">🇺🇬</span>
            <div class="info"><h4>Uganda</h4><p>Future Expansion</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="country-item">
            <span class="flag">🇪🇹</span>
            <div class="info"><h4>Ethiopia</h4><p>Future Expansion</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="country-item">
            <span class="flag">🇸🇴</span>
            <div class="info"><h4>Somalia</h4><p>Future Expansion</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="country-item">
            <span class="flag">🇷🇼</span>
            <div class="info"><h4>Rwanda</h4><p>Future Expansion</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="country-item">
            <span class="flag">🇧🇮</span>
            <div class="info"><h4>Burundi</h4><p>Future Expansion</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="country-item">
            <span class="flag">🇹🇿</span>
            <div class="info"><h4>Tanzania</h4><p>Future Expansion</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="focus-map fade-in">
          <div class="map-placeholder">
            <div class="ring"></div>
            <div class="ring"></div>
            <div class="ring"></div>
            <div class="map-text">
              <span class="big">1</span>
              <span class="sub">Active &bull; 6 in regional vision</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Impact Stories -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Impact Areas</div>
      <div class="section-title">Where Clean Water Changes Everything</div>
      <div class="section-subtitle">Access to clean water creates a ripple effect that transforms entire communities.</div>
      <div class="impact-areas fade-in">
        <div class="impact-area">
          <div class="area-icon">🏥</div>
          <h3>Health</h3>
          <p>Reducing waterborne diseases like cholera, typhoid, and diarrhea — especially among children under 5 who are most vulnerable to contaminated water sources.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-area">
          <div class="area-icon">📚</div>
          <h3>Education</h3>
          <p>When children don't have to walk hours for water, they attend school. Clean water access directly increases school attendance and academic performance, especially for girls.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-area">
          <div class="area-icon">💼</div>
          <h3>Economic Growth</h3>
          <p>Clean water frees up productive hours, reduces healthcare costs, and enables small businesses. The economic multiplier of water access is estimated at 4x return on investment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-area">
          <div class="area-icon">👩</div>
          <h3>Gender Equality</h3>
          <p>Women and girls bear the disproportionate burden of water collection. Access to clean water returns hours to their day — time for education, work, and community leadership.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SDG Alignment -->
  <section class="bg-sand">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">Global Framework</div>
      <div class="section-title">Aligned with the Sustainable Development Goals</div>
      <div class="section-subtitle">Our work directly contributes to 6 of the United Nations Sustainable Development Goals — a framework recognised by every major institutional funder.</div>
      <div class="sdg-grid fade-in">
        <div class="sdg-item">
          <div class="sdg-number">SDG 6</div>
          <h4>Clean Water & Sanitation</h4>
          <p>Our core mission — ensuring availability and sustainable management of water for all.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sdg-item">
          <div class="sdg-number">SDG 3</div>
          <h4>Good Health & Well-being</h4>
          <p>Reducing waterborne diseases through quality testing and safe water education.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sdg-item">
          <div class="sdg-number">SDG 5</div>
          <h4>Gender Equality</h4>
          <p>Freeing women and girls from the burden of water collection — time for school and work.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sdg-item">
          <div class="sdg-number">SDG 10</div>
          <h4>Reduced Inequalities</h4>
          <p><a href="/majimap/">MajiMap</a> exposes water pricing inequality, advocating for fair access regardless of income.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sdg-item">
          <div class="sdg-number">SDG 11</div>
          <h4>Sustainable Cities</h4>
          <p>Improving urban water management through the <a href="https://mimaji.co.ke" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MiMaji platform</a> and data-driven advocacy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sdg-item">
          <div class="sdg-number">SDG 13</div>
          <h4>Climate Action</h4>
          <p>Building water resilience in communities most vulnerable to climate change impacts.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Targets Framework -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-label">2026–2027 Targets</div>
      <div class="section-title">Our Measurable Goals</div>
      <div class="section-subtitle">We measure what matters. These targets guide our work and will be updated with actuals as field data comes in.</div>
      <div class="targets-grid fade-in">
        <div class="target-card">
          <div class="target-metric">10,000</div>
          <div class="target-label">People reached through water testing and education programmes &mdash; <strong>target</strong></div>
        </div>
        <div class="target-card">
          <div class="target-metric">50</div>
          <div class="target-label">Communities with water quality data on <a href="/majimap/">MajiMap</a> &mdash; <strong>target</strong></div>
        </div>
        <div class="target-card">
          <div class="target-metric">50</div>
          <div class="target-label">Schools in the <a href="/water-in-schools/">WASH education programme</a> &mdash; <strong>target</strong></div>
        </div>
        <div class="target-card">
          <div class="target-metric">1</div>
          <div class="target-label">Country with active pilot programme &mdash; <strong>Kenya, Phase 1</strong></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="download-cta fade-in">
        <p>Our detailed impact methodology and data collection framework will be published in our first Annual Impact Report.</p>
        <a href="/resources/" class="btn btn-outline-dark">View Resources &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="section-title">Be Part of the Impact</div>
    <p>Every partnership amplifies our reach. Every contribution accelerates our mission. Join us in making clean water a reality for every community.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/take-action/" class="btn btn-white">Take Action &rarr;</a>
      <a href="https://mimaji.co.ke" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline">Explore MiMaji Platform</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .impact-areas {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .impact-area {
    padding: 2.2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--white);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .impact-area:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(10, 94, 181, 0.1);
  }

  .area-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .impact-area h3 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .impact-area p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .impact-areas {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .sdg-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .targets-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .sdg-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .sdg-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .sdg-item {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--white);
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .sdg-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(10, 94, 181, 0.08);
  }

  .sdg-number {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .sdg-item h4 {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .sdg-item p {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .sdg-item a {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .targets-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .target-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .target-metric {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--blue);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .target-label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .target-label a {
    color: var(--blue);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .target-bar {
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--blue-light);
    border-radius: 3px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .target-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--teal), var(--blue));
    border-radius: 3px;
    transition: width 1s ease;
  }

  .download-cta {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .download-cta p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  /* Vision image */
  .vision-image {
    margin-top: 0;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 50px rgba(10, 94, 181, 0.12);
  }

  .vision-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .image-caption {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--white);
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Honest callout */
  .honest-callout {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: var(--white);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
  }

  .honest-callout p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .honest-callout p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .honest-lead {
    font-size: 1.05rem !important;
    color: var(--blue-deep) !important;
  }

  .honest-callout strong {
    color: var(--blue-deep);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
